cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to identify word sense changes over time. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves clustering and network analysis, which are common techniques in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of unsupervised learning and deep learning models for semantic search and word sense disambiguation also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DL (Machine Learning).
